Hector Mapping Process

1. roscore
2. Connect Hokuyo
#3. sudo chmod a+rw /dev/hokuyo
4. rosrun hokuyo_node hokuyo_node
5. roslaunch hector_slam_launch dvz_test.launch
5. rviz
6. Add map in rviz
	Topic is /scanmatcher_map
	
Save the map
1. rosrun map_server map_saver -f mymap /map:=/scanmatcher_map
	saves map as mymap.yaml in the current directory
